{"tid":866500,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"剛剛發佈的MATE 20系列恐成華為手機的滑鐵盧","createTime":"2018-10-18T02:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T12:02:45.000Z","uid":73695,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"a40697fde7fc4cb5e85154cad51ec0359fd7d085","tid":866500,"uid":73695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T02:24:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chiphell.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=1919115&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;mobile=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chiphell.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D1919115%26extra%3Dpage%253D1%26mobile%3D2&d=u4stnqq8vOcMSVos4gNuvUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f5a7fca8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chiphell.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=1919115&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;mobile=2</a><br />\n<br />\n北京時間10月16日晚21：00（倫敦14：00），華為Mate 20系列於倫敦全球首發。作為7nm麒麟980芯片的首發旗艦，華為Mate 20系列自然集萬千目光於一身，而余承東在蘋果新iPhone發佈會後一句「穩了」，更是為該場發佈會創造了更多想象空間。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/101535_c9d5a8bcd32794de50a29793539c5f91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F101535_c9d5a8bcd32794de50a29793539c5f91.png&h=cb447b80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;然而英國倫敦發佈的mate20系列，作為華為今年下半年的重量級產品，卻有很多網友卻表示沒有購買的意向。經過一番調查，絕大多數人不選擇購買的原因是價格太大，有這個錢還不如買三星蘋果。還有一部分人不購買的原因是太像蘋果了，從劉海到快充到無線充到拍照到配色，簡直就是山寨蘋果，還有就是對華為產品的不信任等等原因<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/101741_19ddd199472a061724da1ea43d437977.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F101741_19ddd199472a061724da1ea43d437977.png&h=43c7d005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（數據來源：CHH）<br />\n小編現在為大家總結下大家對mate20系列失望之處供大家參考<br />\n1、價格上漲&mdash;&mdash;去年Mate 10 6+64GB 699歐元、Mate 10 Pro 6+128GB 799歐元，今年Mate 20&nbsp;&nbsp;4GB+128GB 定價 799 歐元，6GB+128GB 售價 849 歐元、Mate 20X 6+128GB 899歐元、Mate 20 Pro 6GB+128GB 1029 歐元，整體看大約漲價200歐元，約1500元人民幣都可以買個小米8青春版玩耍了！<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n2、花式減配&mdash;&mdash;減配這個詞我們在汽車行業比較常見，其實IT屆也有減配大神，相信大家都知道GPU黃老闆，刀法如神刀刀割肉，不過我們今天欣賞的是余老闆拳拳生風的拳法；<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 首先同樣的「浴霸」不同樣的鏡頭，相比mate20 pro 的 800 萬像素傳感器（ 3 倍長焦，支持 OIS，f/2.4光圈） + 4000 萬像素傳感器（f/1.8 光圈廣角） + 2000 萬像素傳感器（超大廣角、f/2.2 光圈和 16mm 焦距等效）mate20生生被余老闆打成了1200 萬像素傳感器 + 1600 萬像素傳感器 + 800 萬像素傳感器（f/2.4）的組合，整體來看其硬件規格上相比 Pro 機型都有很大的縮水。<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/101754_9a5f310188a92669296eb48692825b97.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F101754_9a5f310188a92669296eb48692825b97.png&h=d6872dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 再說屏幕，mate20 pro採用2K級別的oled屏幕，各類參數也比較喜人，但發佈會上沒有給出自哪家廠家，可是網絡上現在已經爆出第一供貨商來自京東方，第二供貨商來自LG，而且京東方應該也是第一次量產這麼大的2K oled，實際顯示效果不知跟LG的屏幕有多大的出入，難道消費者又要抽獎了？emmc笑而不語，ufs冷眼旁觀；MATE20 採用lcd屏幕估計oled眼瞎黨又要高呼萬歲了，別高興太早該lcd採用rgbw縮水屏，ppi相當於普通RGB的90%,並且畫面更佳慘白，所以先歇歇等著各家評測後再看！讓屏幕再飛一會undefined<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/101817_9f6b1b6bdf947faeecf50be027c3461e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F101817_9f6b1b6bdf947faeecf50be027c3461e.png&h=55460b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(左側mate20 pro 右側mate20 )"},{"pid":"e568aeef54582f9f5992452ced11843a4a043436","tid":866500,"uid":73695,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T02:25:03.000Z","msg":"下面我們再說說電池和充電，發佈會上拳王余各種花式炫耀，4200mAh啊、40w快充啊、15w無線充電啊等等，對了還有逆天的無線反向快充技術，也就是無線「充電寶」，兩部手機就是一部永動機了呢，呵呵；但實際這些都是mate20通通沒有,都被打掉了，mate20 只擁有4000mAh電池，僅支持普通的快充（超級快充4.5V/5A兼容5V/4.5A），更不支持無線充電了&hellip;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 還沒完呢，mate20相比mate20 pro 缺少屏下指紋和3D 面部識別功能，更驚喜的是mate20 pro 6G內存版本居然沒有屏下指紋解鎖，僅僅只有高價的8G內存版本才會有，真精彩；mate20（1個全頻揚聲器+1個高音揚聲器）相比mate20pro（雙立體聲揚聲器） 在揚聲器上也略有不同。<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/101857_78cb51ab7a6d9e7da8271f5a95b7781b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F101857_78cb51ab7a6d9e7da8271f5a95b7781b.png&h=0a9b1e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 筆者心累就不說那些IP68進水不保修、不支持聯通VoLTE、非雙通、電信不能雙4G待機的這類小事情&hellip;大家自己挖掘其他內容可以留言，真是【浴霸】不能&hellip;跟iphone比劉海寬度，跟遊戲機比續航，跟iphone比續航&hellip;PPT好評<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/101912_3f478e1a7fc759a5654903d0d3086123.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F101912_3f478e1a7fc759a5654903d0d3086123.png&h=0610ce7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;雖然華為目前在國內很強勢，但一味地跟風抄襲注定會走向滅亡，華為向來以國內科技企業龍頭老大自居，但事實真的是這樣嘛?大多數普通人都會在心裡悄悄地打個問號。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">華而不實 為所欲為</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547c14c001a356e30d85096f4fd69ca66063cee4","tid":866500,"uid":41818,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"「歐洲大把人用」"},{"pid":"b44f94a3f39cc7f9f89c1c2d69a10e4b9307f9c7","tid":866500,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:56:42.000Z","msg":"每要多一個功能，就要捱多一刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2441c476b0fc5558fabedc24863166601ec7bb7","tid":866500,"uid":36551,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.an